		<div id="comment_body_64210634">Something that gets too little attention is what the <a href="https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Ocean_acidification" title="wikipedia.org">added carbon</a> [wikipedia.org] is doing to our oceans.  And while a solar shade might lower the temperature on the planet, it won't do anything to slow, let alone reverse, the damage from lower pH in the oceans.</div>
	</div>

